  "f5795650-ed68-4850-a36f-622e01abe3c2"],
 "\n     Caution: Mathematica now considers all of these symbols to be \
constants\n     For very simple expressions, Mathematica erroneously \
integrates the 'constants'\n          If that happens, must omit /.rulesDisp. \
The expressions should be almost as readable\n          For example, might \
get  ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubsuperscriptBox["\[Integral]", "1", "r"], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"6d8729fe-b7ff-4dba-9e34-05f51719d742"],
