the numerator and a double integral in the denominator. Checking whether or \
not the remaining equation, \!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(R\), \(11\)]\), is an \
identity when using this expression is too computationally intensive for my \
home computer.\>\"", "]"}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
