Cell[BoxData["\<\"Plugging back in, the equations are too lengthy to include \
here. However, \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(11\\)]\\)-\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(44\\)]\\) = 0, so the LHS can \
be put over a common denominator and then the denominator can be discarded. \
The  resulting LHS has a factor of \
(2\[GothicCapitalC]+\\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[\\\"r\[GothicCapitalC]\\\", \\\"\
\[Prime]\\\",MultilineFunction->None]\\)), so we can easily find at least one \
solution:\"\>"], "Print",
