$CellContext`\[ScriptCapitalA]^(-1) OverDot[$CellContext`a, 1]^2/
    Subscript[$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD], 
     4] + $CellContext`a^(-1) $CellContext`c^2 \
$CellContext`\[ScriptCapitalA]^(-1) OverDot[$CellContext`a, 2]/
    Subscript[$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD], 4] + 
   Rational[-1, 
      2] $CellContext`a^(-1) $CellContext`c^2 \
$CellContext`\[ScriptCapitalA]^(-2) OverDot[$CellContext`a, 1] 
