     3 $CellContext`c^2 $CellContext`\[Kappa] $CellContext`\[CapitalKappa]^2 - \
$CellContext`a[$CellContext`t]^2 + 
     2 $CellContext`\[CapitalKappa] $CellContext`\[CapitalLambda] \
