Cell[BoxData["\<\"As usual, when we re-do a case with an additional \
assumption, we \\!\\(\\*StyleBox[\\\"could\\\",FontSlant->\\\"Italic\\\"]\\) \
obtain another solution. In this case, we \
\\!\\(\\*StyleBox[\\\"do\\\",FontSlant->\\\"Italic\\\"]\\) obtain a new \
solution. We are re-doing Case d with the assumption that \
\[ScriptCapitalA](t) = 1; i.e., A(t,r) = \[ScriptCapitalA](t) \
\[CapitalAlpha](r) = \[CapitalAlpha](r).\"\>"], "Print",
